Hello:



You need to build the Cantera interface library with your Fortran compiler.
This library source also includes 2 C++ files so you will also need a C/C++
compiler that works with your Fortran compiler.  I seem to remember that
Visual Studion 6 works with the various Compaq Fortran 6.x versions. 



The source is located in the zip under: &#39;cantera/Cantera/fortran/src&#39;





